    {"type": "rectangle", "id": "tech-comments", "x": 60, "y": 680, "width": 1100, "height": 260, "strokeColor": "#455a64", "strokeWidth": 1, "fillStyle": "dashed", "backgroundColor": "#eceff1", "roughness": 0, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "tech-comments-text"}]},
    {"type": "text", "id": "tech-comments-text", "x": 70, "y": 690, "width": 1080, "height": 240, "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "Technical Details:\n\nIngestion Flow:\n1. ScraperOrchestrator.run() iterates enabled sources (NSE, SEBI)\n2. For each source: detect_new(from_date, to_date) returns ScrapeDetectionResult\n3. For each detected circular: upsert_circular() → update_status() → _download_assets()\n4. _download_assets() detects ZIP vs PDF, extracts if needed, stores in data/regulatory_raw/SOURCE/YYYY/MM/\n5. Status transitions: DISCOVERED → FETCHED (or FAILED)\n\nIndexing Flow (run-indexer):\n1. ElasticsearchIndexer.run_once() fetches pending records with status FETCHED\n2. For each record: list_assets() → PDFTextExtractor.extract() → FixedSizeChunker.chunk()\n3. If ES_ENABLE_CONTEXTUAL_RETRIEVAL=true: Contextualizer.contextualize_chunks() per chunk\n4. EmbeddingProvider.embed_texts() generates 768-dim BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5 vectors\n5. ElasticsearchClient.bulk_index() ingests all chunks into ES index\n6. circular_repository.mark_es_indexed() updates PostgreSQL es_indexed_at, es_chunk_count\nSearch Flow (RAG):\n1. ElasticsearchClient.search() runs BM25 and KNN queries in parallel (size=40 each)\n2. RRF fusion via ranx library: rrf([bm25_run, knn_run], k=60) re-ranks results\n3. Top 40 fused hits returned as list[SearchHit]\n4. RAGAnswerGenerator.generate_answer() builds prompt with top 10 chunks\n5. LLM (minimax-m2.7) generates answer with citations, max_tokens=4000\n\nConfiguration (config.py):\n• ES_CHUNK_SIZE=800, ES_CHUNK_OVERLAP=150 | ES_INDEXER_BATCH_SIZE=50\n• ES_VECTOR_DIMS=768, ES_EMBEDDING_MODEL=BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5\n• ES_ENABLE_CONTEXTUAL_RETRIEVAL=true, ES_CONTEXTUAL_MODEL=minimaxai/minimax-m2.7, ES_CONTEXTUAL_MAX_TOKENS=500\n• ES_RRF_WINDOW_SIZE=50, ES_RRF_RANK_CONSTANT=60 (ranx library)\n• RAG_MODEL=minimaxai/minimax-m2.7, RAG_MAX_CHUNKS=10, RAG_MAX_TOKENS=4000\n• ELASTICSEARCH_URL=http://localhost:9200, ES_SEARCH_DEFAULT_STRATEGY=hybrid", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 160, "containerId": "tech-comments", "roughness": 0, "roundness": null, "strokeStyle": "solid"}
  ],
  "files": {},
  "appState": {"gridSize": null, "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"}
